title: The WomTrend King 9/16: Bad Bunny, Martha's Vineyard, Jeffrey Dahmer, SNL, 'Dont Worry Darling'

description:
In this edition of The WomTrend King, Jack and super producer Becca discuss Bad Bunny's new music video, the Right's inability to see asylum seekers as humans, the new Jeffrey Dahmer show, the new SNL cast members, and the NYT's 'Don"t Worry Darling' review!
